# 用户自定义拦截规则 (User Custom Reject Rules)
# 格式: classical text | behavior: classical
# 用途: 强制阻断不希望访问的域名/IP（REJECT-DROP）
# 维护: https://github.com/haoliangli/ray-clash-rules

# ---- 手动封锁站点 ----
# DOMAIN-SUFFIX,updates.devmate.com
# DOMAIN-SUFFIX,sparkle.pdfexpert.com
# DOMAIN-SUFFIX,aodo365.com
# DOMAIN-SUFFIX,better365.cn

# ------------------------------------------------------------
# 1. 强力关键词封锁（仅限极高确信度）
# ------------------------------------------------------------
DOMAIN-KEYWORD,bitcoin
DOMAIN-KEYWORD,blockchain
DOMAIN-KEYWORD,crypto
DOMAIN-KEYWORD,cryptocurrency
DOMAIN-KEYWORD,defi
DOMAIN-KEYWORD,web3

